there's that embodiment,

922
01:09:58,894 --> 01:10:01,727
um, our own unique embodiments.

923
01:10:01,797 --> 01:10:06,666
And then there's disability
which is basically the-

924
01:10:06,735 --> 01:10:12,367
the... social repression
