964
01:12:33,349 --> 01:12:35,909
Okay. Um, so it's by weight.

965
01:12:35,984 --> 01:12:37,918
Oh, it's by weight?
Can we guess?

966
01:12:37,986 --> 01:12:40,682
I can probably just do it
